  "text": "Face recognition experiments have been performed on the ORL and AR face databases. Due to the high dimensionality of the data, conventional GA-based feature extraction methods like EP [CITATION_1] and EDA [CITATION_2] cannot be directly applied to these two databases unless reducing the dimensionality in advance. By contraries, the EDFE and BEDFE algorithms proposed in this paper can still work very well with them.",
